title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Nov 29 2021
itunes:title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Nov 29 2021
description:
Omicron fear-mongering begins with travel bans - the same ones that were supposedly racist under Trump. Jussie Smollett trial for fake MAGA attack begins today. How will the media cover it? Arizona State students protest to get Kyle Rittenhouse booted from school. Alex Berenson weighs in on the new Omicron variant and why it's not time to panic. How the media is treating the Waukesha story and ignoring some obvious facts.
